<div class="definition" id="definition-B" acro="B" titletext="Basis">
<h5 class="definition">
<span class="type">Definition </span><span class="acro">B</span> <span class="titletext"> Basis</span>
</h5>
<p>Suppose $V$ is a vector space.  Then a subset $S\subseteq V$ is a <em class="term">basis</em> of $V$ if it is linearly independent and spans $V$.</p>
